<p>Jo’s cover design for <em>Soft Core</em> is cunty, luxe and so stylish—I love it.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="https://www.kishanrajanidesign.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Kishan Rajani</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780593535349" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263962" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-173-best-book-covers-of-2025/aubyn-parallel-lines/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/aubyn-parallel-lines.jpg" data-orig-size="1000,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="aubyn parallel lines" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Edward St. Aubyn, &lt;em&gt;Parallel Lines&lt;/em&gt;; cover design by Jack Smyth (Knopf, June)&lt;/p&gt;
