<p>Title type dances with art that splits the author&#8217;s name! Appreciate all the bold design choices.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="https://www.stephenbrayda.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Stephen Brayda</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781324021605" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="257583" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-11-best-book-covers-of-july/81iefl81j5l-_sl1500_/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_.jpg" data-orig-size="988,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="strata" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Laura Poppick, &lt;a href=&quot;https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781324021605&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;&lt;em&gt;Strata: Stories from Deep Time&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/a&gt;; cover design by Steve Attardo (Norton, July)&lt;/p&gt;
" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-198x300.jpg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-674x1024.jpg" class="size-full wp-image-257583" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_.jpg" alt="strata" width="988" height="1500" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_.jpg 988w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-198x300.jpg 198w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-674x1024.jpg 674w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-768x1166.jpg 768w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-40x60.jpg 40w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/07/81IEfL81j5L._SL1500_-33x50.jpg 33w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 988px) 100vw, 988px" /></a> Laura Poppick, <a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9781324021605" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external"><em>Strata: Stories from Deep Time</em></a>; cover design by Steve Attardo (Norton, July)</span>
<p>This cover is smart, elegant, and breathes with the perfect amount of white space. The title font, with its subtle slant, pairs perfectly with the slant of the colorful image below.</p>
<p style="text-align: right;"><em>–<a href="http://notchdesign.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="external">Derek Thornton</a></em></p>
<span class="caption"><a href="https://bookshop.org/a/132/9780593803738" class="external" target="_blank"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="263951" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/the-173-best-book-covers-of-2025/gish-jen-bad-bad-girl/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2025/12/Gish-Jen-Bad-Bad-Girl.jpg" data-orig-size="987,1500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="Gish Jen, Bad Bad Girl" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="&lt;p&gt;Gish Jen, &lt;em&gt;Bad Bad Girl&lt;em&gt;; cover design by Linda Huang (Knopf, October)&lt;/p&gt;
